findings.title: Deployer can collect tokens from contract
findings.description: The deployer has the capability to collect tokens from the smart contract.

findings.title: Deployer can set fees with an indefinite amount
findings.description: The deployer has the capability to set fees without any limitations or restrictions, potentially leading to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Deployer can renounce ownership
findings.description: The deployer has the capability to renounce ownership of the contract, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Deployer can transfer ownership
findings.description: The deployer has the capability to transfer ownership of the contract, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Deployer can change address receivers
findings.description: The deployer has the capability to alter the address of token receivers.

findings.title: Deployer can block users from trading
findings.description: The deployer has the capability to restrict users from performing trades.
